    ├── pentachoric_decoder_simulation.py
    ├── gateaware_decoder_simulation.py
    ├── e6_syndrome_decoder_simulation.py
    ├── noise_model_decomposition.py
    └── threshold_sweep_simulation.py

pf_gate_simulation.py          ← fully self-contained
