## Reproducing Paper Results

Each appendix in the paper opens with a status line identifying the script(s) that produced its results. For example:

> **Appendix D:** "All results are reproducible from lattice_scaling_simulation.py and optimal_gate_assignment.py."

Running the named script(s) reproduces the tables reported in that appendix.

