## Key Results

| Result | Script | Finding |
|--------|--------|---------|
| Dynamic detection rate | `dynamic_pentachoric_simulation.py` | 95.1% overall, 100% central (τ ≥ 5) |
| Detection scaling | `lattice_scaling_simulation.py` | 95.1% → 98.0% → 98.9% at 7/19/37 nodes |
| Optimal detection floor | `optimal_gate_assignment.py` | 100% (no single-error blind spots) |
| Gate-aware correction | `gateaware_decoder_simulation.py` | 96.4% correction fidelity at 37 nodes |
| Composite suppression | `noise_model_decomposition.py` | 500–1,800× (three levels combined) |
| Fault-tolerance threshold | `threshold_sweep_simulation.py` | ~5% (Level 2), ~7–12% (Levels 1+2) |
| Qubit subspace confinement | `pf_gate_simulation.py` | {Rₓ, Rz} phase drift = exactly 0 after 1,000 gates |
| F gate depth advantage | `native_algorithm_benchmarks.py` | O(d) → O(1) per long-range interaction |

